## **MOSC tenant-only (local)**

```powershell
# Full MOSC tenant block
F:\project_workspace\mosc-temp\code_html_template\batch_files\database_export_import_refresh.bat F:\project_workspace CONTAINER_ID /REGEN-MOSC /SKIP-EXPORT /IMPORT-FILE "F:\project_workspace\mosc-temp\code_html_template\SQLS\corrected_event_media_inserts.ordered.mosc_malankara_orthodox_2.sql" /FORCE

# Fast dup-only refresh (no schema rebuild)
F:\project_workspace\mosc-temp\code_html_template\batch_files\database_export_import_refresh.bat F:\project_workspace CONTAINER_ID /REGEN-MOSC /SKIP-EXPORT /DATA-ONLY /IMPORT-DUP-ONLY /FORCE
```

See §1c in [DATABASE_EXPORT_IMPORT_GUIDE.html](mdc:documentation/database_export_import/DATABASE_EXPORT_IMPORT_GUIDE.html).

