## **Verification**

```powershell
docker exec CONTAINER_ID psql -U event_site_admin -d event_site_manager_db -c "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_calendar_entry;"
docker exec CONTAINER_ID psql -U event_site_admin -d event_site_manager_db -c "SELECT MAX(id) FROM executive_committee_team_members; SELECT last_value FROM executive_committee_team_members_id_seq;"
```

After import, each `{table}_id_seq.last_value` should be ≥ `MAX(id)` for that table. Details: [sequence_id_alignment_and_import.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/sequence_id_alignment_and_import.mdc).

